{
  "text": "Numerous studies have investigated the consumption of antimicrobials in hospitalised adult patients by using DDDs, but such studies in paediatric patients are in large scale missing [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
  "correct_citation": {
